I"è<p>A Jekyll theme for blogging. With built in category sorting and author
blocks,  this theme is perfect for collaborative projects.</p>

<h1 id="how-to-use-it">How to use it</h1>
<ol>
  <li>Star &amp; fork the <a href="http://github.com/ninapetrop/Jekyll-Testing-Site">repo</a></li>
  <li>Rename the repo and clone the master branch to your local directory</li>
  <li>Customize the <code>_config.yml</code> file to represent you</li>
  <li>Download <a href="https://github.com/gulpjs/gulp/blob/master/docs/getting-started.md">Gulp</a></li>
</ol>

<hr />
<p>See any of the posts in this theme for instructions on the author block
and category pages.</p>

